  Returns whether the given argument is an array.

  @function up.util.isArray
  @param object
  @return {Boolean}
  @stable
  ###
  # https://developer.mozilla.org/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/isArray
  isArray = Array.isArray || 
